{"tid":2051242,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：議員滋擾行為證明目前23條立法已無可能","createTime":"2020-06-04T15:26:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T16:02:58.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6efa5b18bbc18f1caa69d93a8fae3fab23a2829b","tid":2051242,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T15:26:42.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥在社交網站帖文，指3名非建制派議員，今日在立法會投擲惡臭不明物體的滋擾性行為，證明以立法會目前的亂象，要落實《基本法》第23條的本地立法已經無可能。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又說，國歌法要折騰半年才能通過，相信長期被「别有用心的人」污名化、妖魔化的23條，更難以通過立法會，她反問社會是否可以容忍暴力不斷上升、危害國家安全風險增加，認為「港區國安法」是回應大部分市民的期望，呼籲市民就人大常委會的立法工作踴躍發表意見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1299731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1299731&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EgUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=044ccdde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1299731</a>"},{"pid":"0d7ec043ba68a3859cc765cbaa3da21d853a7f2b","tid":2051242,"uid":286897,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T15:28:18.000Z","msg":"好嘢<br />\n原來上去係加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲整個國安法摧毀舊香港<br />\n我哋先可以建立新香港"},{"pid":"c1b05e7fd0b99dcb81c230bd38df426f0eb46f5c","tid":2051242,"uid":132587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T15:30:18.000Z","msg":"點解佢覺得23條無可能 國歌法要半年<br />\n但國安法又無問題?"},{"pid":"cfb549d4243af3d7245feeeb08a708db5f90c088","tid":2051242,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T15:31:00.000Z","msg":"條臭閪想卸膊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"